div.p:
For the proofe of which I thus argue;



                        Judas his conſpiracy began from the Devils entring into him, which was when he received the ſop at the Supper in John 13.


                        But Judas his conſpiracy began from Bethany;



                        Therefore the Devils entering into him, when he received the ſop at the ſupper in John 13. was at Bethany.
